    S5 -.-> Q5["Recruiter questions<br><br>• What makes your MLOps experience real?<br>• How did you handle point-in-time correctness and leakage?<br>• How did release/rollback become governed?"]
    S6 -.-> Q6["Recruiter questions<br><br>• What made this more than a technical demo?<br>• What day-2 / incident evidence existed?<br>• Did you treat cost like a real engineering constraint?"]
